ina)Nomoclastidae,(Protimesius,Stygnoplus,Stygnidius,Gaibulus,Stygnus,Pickeliana,Eutimesius)Stygnidae,(Pseudotrogulus,Ogloblinia,Acutisoma,Iguapeia,Tumbesia,Sodreana,Arthrodes,Iporangaia,Gerdesius,Multumbo,Sadocus,Megapachylus,Triglochinura,Discocyrtus,Fonckia,Pseudogyndesoides,Pachylospeleus,Daguerreia,Hernandaria,Huralvioides,Acanthoprocta,Oliverius,Pachylus,Mischonyx,Longiperna,Goodnightiella,Hyperpachylus,Bourguyia,Ischnotherus,Liogonyleptoides,Encheiridium,Piassagera,Gonyleptoides,Roeweria,Neoancistrotus,Mitogoniella,Metagonyleptes,Progonyleptoidellus,Gonyleptes,Metagyndes,Trichominua,Eusarcus,Neogonyleptes,Parapachyloides,Metamitobates,Promitobates,Ampheres,Carlotta,Rhioxyna,Pachyloides,Despirus,Hypophyllonomus,Discocyrtoides,Heteropachylus,Graphinotus,Goniosoma,Ruschia,Metarthrodes,Holoversia,Parampheres,Pristocnemus,Acanthogonyleptes,Neosadocus,Hutamaia,Glysterus,Magnispina,Cobania,Serracutisoma,Mitopernoides,Adhynastes,Acanthopachylus,Gonyleptellus,Geraecormobius,Mitobates,Junicus,Pseudopucrolia,Pseudopachylus)Gonyleptidae,(Texella,Proscotolemon,Sitalcina,Megacina,unclassified_Phalangodidae,Bishopella,Crosbyella,Scotolemon,Turquinia,Phalangodes,Calicina,Wespus,Tolus,Pseudobiantes,Remyus,Undulus,Banksula)Phalangodidae,(Metasarcus,Tapacochana,Incasarcus,Napostygnus,Cajamarca)Metasarcidae,unclassified_Gonyleptoidea)Gonyleptoidea,((Pirassunungoleptes,Zalmoxis,Pachylicus,Parascotolemon,unclassified_Zalmoxidae,Ethobunus,Guagonia,Urachiche,Phalangodinella)Zalmoxidae,(unclassified_Kimulidae,Kimula,Minuella,Relictopiolus,Tegipiolus)Kimulidae,(Guasinia)Guasiniidae,unclassified_Zalmoxoidea,(Fissiphallius)Fissiphalliidae,(unclassified_Escadabiidae,Baculigerus,Brotasus,Escadabius)Escadabiidae,(Icaleptes)Icaleptidae)Zalmoxoidea,((Mysorea,Trionyxella)Trionyxellidae,(Paktongius,Bandona,Arulla,Dampetrus,Seuthes,Neopygoplus,Tarnus,Chilon,unclassified_Assamiidae)Assamiidae)Assamioidea,((Badessa,Hummelinckiolus,Pellobunus)Samoidae,(Metabiantes,Lacurbs,Hinzuanius)Biantidae,(Sty ia,Myrmecocystus,Teratomyrmex,Lasius,Anoplolepis,Prolasius,Euprenolepis,Paraparatrechina,Paratrechina,Lasiophanes,Pseudolasius,Acropyga,Nylanderia)Lasiini,(Agraulomyrmex,Plagiolepis,Tapinolepis,Lepisiota,Stigmacros)Plagiolepidini,(Myrmelachista)Myrmelachistini,(Santschiella,Gesomyrmex)Gesomyrmecini,(Polyergus,Iberoformica,Cataglyphis,Proformica,Formica,Rossomyrmex,Bajcaridris)Formicini,(Oecophylla)Oecophyllini,(Colobopsis,Calomyrmex,Notostigma,Polyrhachis,Opisthopsis,Phasmomyrmex,Forelophilus,Camponotus,Echinopla)Camponotini,(Myrmoteras)Myrmoteratini,unclassified_Formicinae,(Brachymyrmex,Aphomomyrmex,Cladomyrma,Petalomyrmex)Brachymyrmecini,(Gigantiops)Gigantiopini,(Myrmecorhynchus,Melophorus,Notoncus)Melophorini)Formicinae,(Tetraponera,Pseudomyrmex,Myrcidris)Pseudomyrmecinae,((Phaulomyrma,Leptanilla,Yavnella)Leptanillini,(Protanilla,Anomalomyrma)Anomalomyrmini)Leptanillinae)Formicidae)Formicoidea,((Stenotritus,Ctenocolletes)Stenotritidae,(unclassified_Apidae,((Manuelia)Manueliini,(Ceratina)Ceratinini,(Xylocopa)Xylocopini,(Brevineura,Eucondylops,Exoneura,Allodapula,Allodape,Exoneuridia,Inquilina,Macrogalea,Compsomelissa,Hasinamelissa,Braunsapis,Exoneurella,Halterapis,Nasutapis)Allodapini)Xylocopinae,(Unclassified_Bombinae,(Bombus)Bombini,(Exaerete,Euglossa,Eufriesea,Eulaema,Aglae)Euglossini)Bombinae,((Ancyla,Tarsalia)Ancylini,(Nanorhathymus,Rhathymus)Rhathymini,(Tetrapedia,Coelioxoides)Tetrapediini,(Thyreus,Xeromelecta,Melecta,Zacosmia,Tetralonioidella)Melectini,(Melissodes,Simanthedon,Martinapis,Santiago,Unclassified_Eucerini,Eucerinoda,Melissoptila,Svastrina,Alloscirtetica,Trichocerapis,Svastrides,Mirnapis,Thygater,Eucera,Svastra,Canephorula,Florilegus)Eucerini,(Isepeolus,Melectoides)Isepeolini,(Leiopodus)Protepeolini,(Tropidopedia,Tapinotaspis,Trigonopedia,Tapinotaspoides,unclassified_Tapinotaspidini,Chalepogenus,Nasutopedia,Lanthanomelissa,Arhysoceble,Paratetrapedia,Xanthopedia,Monoeca,Lophopedia,Caenonomada,Urbanapis)Tapinotaspidini,(Anthophorula,Exomalopsis,Chi
